# Superstore Sales Analysis

## Project Overview

This project analyzes a retail sales dataset using Excel to identify sales patterns and key business insights.

The analysis focuses on:

- Top selling products
- Sales by city
- Monthly sales trend

---

## Dataset

The dataset contains sales transaction data including:

- Order Date
- Product Name
- City
- Category
- Sales

---

## Dashboard

The Excel dashboard includes:

- Top 10 products by sales
- Top 10 cities by sales
- Monthly sales trend

---

## Key Insights

1. Canon ImageCLASS 2200 Advanced Copier is the best-selling product.

2. New York City generates the highest sales among all cities.

3. Sales show a steady increase from 2015 to 2018.

4. Sales tend to peak toward the end of the year.

---

## Tools Used

- Excel
- Pivot Tables
- Pivot Charts
- Data Cleaning
